---
title: Balsamic & Thyme Beef Steak with Veggies & Creamy Mash
description: There is something so comforting about the aroma of caramelised butter, thyme and vinegar bubbling in a pan. Completely mouth-watering to say the least. Drizzled over a hot steak, atop a mound of creamy mashed potato – what’s not to love?
